A2 call: remake (and quarter thru)

Watch carefully the distinction between 'remake' and 'grand remake' from
columns.

sdr> /program = Program.A2 ; setFormation(Formation.SQUARED_SET)
|      3Gv  3Bv
|
| 4B>            2G<
|
| 4G>            2B<
|
|      1B^  1G^
sdr> heads square thru
| 4B>  3G<  3B>  2G<
|
| 4G>  1B<  1G>  2B<
sdr> boys walk girls dodge
| 4G>  4B>  1G>  3B>
|
| 1B<  3G<  2B<  2G<
sdr> /// verify that "cast 1/2" is NOT done grand
sdr> quarter thru
| 1B^  3Gv  4G^  4Bv  2B^  2Gv  1G^  3Bv
sdr> hinge
| 1B>  4G>  2B>  1G>
|
| 3G<  4B<  2G<  3B<
sdr> /// verify that "cast 1/2" part is done grand
sdr> grand quarter thru
| 3G^  4Bv  1B^  2Gv  4G^  3Bv  2B^  1Gv
sdr> hinge
| 3G>  1B>  4G>  2B>
|
| 4B<  2G<  3B<  1G<
sdr> /// verify that "cast 1/2" part is done grand
sdr> grand remake
| 2G>  3B>  1G>  2B>
|
| 4B<  3G<  1B<  4G<
sdr> /// verify that "cast 1/2" part is NOT done grand
sdr> remake
| 3G>  3B>  4G>  2B>
|
| 4B<  2G<  1B<  1G<
sdr> hinge
| 4B^  3Gv  2G^  3Bv  1B^  4Gv  1G^  2Bv
sdr> /program = C4
C4
sdr> /// verify that the final "cast 3/4" part is NOT done grand
sdr> finish left remake
|      4B<            1B<
| 3G^       2Gv  4G^       1Gv
|      3B>            2B>
sdr> left quarter thru
| 4B^  3Gv  2G^  3Bv  1B^  4Gv  1G^  2Bv
sdr> /// verify that the final "cast 3/4" part is done grand
sdr> finish grand left remake
|      4B<  2G<  1B<
| 3G^                 1Gv
|      3B>  4G>  2B>
sdr> go home
|      3Gv  3Bv
|
| 4B>            2G<
|
| 4G>            2B<
|
|      1B^  1G^
sdr> heads square thru ; pass the ocean
| 1B^  3Gv  4G^  4Bv  2B^  2Gv  1G^  3Bv
sdr> /// verify that "cast 1/4" part is NOT done grand
sdr> do 1/3 of a left remake
|      4G<            1G<
| 1B^       4Bv  2B^       3Bv
|      3G>            2G>
sdr> left quarter thru
| 4G^  1Bv  4B^  3Gv  1G^  2Bv  3B^  2Gv
sdr> trade the wave
| 4Bv  3G^  4Gv  1B^  3Bv  2G^  1Gv  2B^
sdr> /// verify that "cast 1/4" part is done grand
sdr> do 1/3 of a grand remake
|      3G>  1B>  2G>
| 4Bv                 2B^
|      4G<  3B<  1G<
sdr> /exit
